answers.answer: Tiredness and headaches - YES YES YES I have them. Among many others.

question: I've been on Cymbalta since Dec of '06 for health anxiety problems. Since then I've had a dry mouth, increased thirst, tiredness, headaches. Anyone else experience this? I am slipping back to worrying again! Stuff like diabetes b/c of some of my symptoms.
title: Cymbalta?
